If you even THINK about calling Vision greedy, think again...<br>
I don't know how many times I have seen people turn down HoT drops, even BPs, to give them to a member who needs it more. In Vision, I am treated fairly, and as an individual who attends raids when he can. I don't know any Vision who would not help me (if available) if I called on them and asked them for their help. <br>
Concerning Vision coming near break-up frequently:<br>
I have been in Vision for over a month, not a long time, but time enough to learn that there is no quarrels within the guild. In the month or so that I've been with the guild, I have seen no one ripping on each other (except if in jest) or saying &quot;I'm gonna leave the guild if things don't shape up soon&quot; or anything of the sort. In my opinion, Vision is a GREAT guild, one that respects its members and is always willing to help. Thank you Vision for letting me participate in this great family.<br>
<br>
<br>
Pinches Pennies<br>
59 Blackguard<br>
